## E) Uso local (desarrollo)

### 1) Dashboard local
```
APP_ENV=local
APP_DEBUG=true
APP_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8010

REMOTE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8001
REMOTE_API_KEY=<GC_API_TOKEN_LOCAL>
```

Arranque:
```bash
php artisan optimize:clear
php artisan serve --host=127.0.0.1 --port=8010
```

### 2) API local (gc-data-api)
En `services/gc-data-api/.env`:
```
APP_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8001
DB_* = Postgres remoto (TCP)
GC_API_TOKEN=<GC_API_TOKEN_LOCAL>
GC_API_CREATED_BY=1
```

Arranque:
```bash
cd services/gc-data-api
php artisan optimize:clear
php artisan serve --host=127.0.0.1 --port=8001
```

Health:
```bash
TOKEN="<GC_API_TOKEN_LOCAL>"
curl -H "X-API-Key: $TOKEN" http://127.0.0.1:8001/api/v1/health
```

